ason|2007]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Major League Soccer|MLS]]\n|5||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||2||1||7||1\n|-\n|[[2008 Major League Soccer season|2008]]\n|25||5||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||0||0||25||5\n|-\n|[[A.C. Milan|Milan]] (loan)\n|[[2008\u201309 A.C. Milan season|2008\u201309]]\n|[[Serie A]]\n|18||2||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||2||0||0||0||20||2\n|-\n|[[LA Galaxy]]\n|[[2009 Los Angeles Galaxy season|2009]]\n|[[Major League Soccer|MLS]]\n|11||2||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||4||0||15||2\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[A.C. Milan|Milan]] (loan)\n|[[2009\u201310 A.C. Milan season|2009\u201310]]\n|[[Serie A]]\n|11||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||2||0||0||0||13||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!29!!2!!0!!0!!colspan=\"2\"|\u2013!!4!!0!!0!!0!!33!!2\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[LA Galaxy]]\n|[[2010 Los Angeles Galaxy season|2010]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Major League Soccer|MLS]]\n|7||2||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||3||0||10||2\n|-\n|[[2011 Los Angeles Galaxy season|2011]]\n|26||2||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||4||0||30||2\n|-\n|[[2012 Los Angeles Galaxy season|2012]]\n|24||7||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||1||6||0||31||8\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!98!!18!!0!!0!!colspan=\"2\"|\u2013!!1!!1!!19!!1!!118!!20\n|-\n|[[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]]\n|[[2012\u201313 Paris Saint-Germain F.C. season|2012\u201313]]\n|[[Ligue 1]]\n|10||0||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||2||0||0||0||14||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!523!!97!!35!!10!!12!!1!!118!!18!!31!!3!!719!!129\n|}\n\n{{reflist|group=Note}}\n\n===International===\n<ref>{{NFT player|id=2189|name=David Beckham|accessdate=10 June 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/beckham-intl.html |title=David Robert Joseph Beckham \u2013 Century of International Appearances |website=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation |date=29 October 2009 |accessdate=10 June 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://soccernet.espn.go