aki Matsumoto]]|JPN}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2001|2001 Akita]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Gennaro Talarico]]|ITA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Takahiro Niki]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Adnan Hadzic (karateka)|Adnan Hadzic]]|BIH}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2005|2005 Duisburg]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[K\u00f6ksal Cakir]]|GER}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Konstantinos Papadopoulos (karateka)|Konstantinos Papadopoulos]]|GRE}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Klaudio Farmadin]]|SVK}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2009|2009 Kaohsiung]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Michail Georgios Tzanos]]|GRE}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Diego Vandeschrick]]|BEL}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Kou Matsuhisa]]|JPN}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2013|2013 Cali]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Rafael Aghayev]]|AZE}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Noah Bitsch]]|GER}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Mohamed Abdelrahman Ali]]|EGY}}\n|-\n| [[2017 World Games|2017 Wroc\u0142aw]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Stanislav Horuna]]|UKR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Ali Asghar Asiabari]]|IRI}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Hern\u00e2ni Ver\u00edssimo]]|BRA}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite \u221280 kg====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1981|1981 Santa Clara]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Osamu Kamikodo]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Hisao Murase]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Tokey Hill]]|USA}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Otti Roethoff]]|NED}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1985|1985 London]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Gianluca Guazzaroni]]|ITA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Pierre Pinar]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Arild Engh]]|NOR}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Mervyn Etienne]]|GBR}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1989|1989 Karlsruhe]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Gianluca Guazzaroni]]|ITA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Kemal Aktepe]]|NED}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Sven Mohnssen]]|FRG}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Ralf Wintergarst]]|FRG}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1993|1993 The Hague]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Augustus Paul]]|GBR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Miko Virkola]]|FIN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Peter Bathoorn]]|NED}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Sami Tainen]]|FIN}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1997|1997 Lahti]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Toshihito Kokubun]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[George Petermann]]|