iner]]|GER}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Cath\u00e9rine Bernard]]|FRA}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1997|1997 Lahti]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Atsuko Wakai]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Roberta Sodero]]|ITA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Cinzia Colaiacomo]]|ITA}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2001|2001 Akita]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Atsuko Wakai]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Yohana S\u00e0nchez]]|VEN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Junko Arai]]|USA}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2005|2005 Duisburg]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Atsuko Wakai]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Myriam Szkudlarek]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Ana Sofia Mart\u00ednez]]|VEN}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2009|2009 Kaohsiung]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Nguyen Hoang Ngan]]|VIE}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Mar\u00eda Dimitrova]]|DOM}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Sara Battaglia (karateka)|Sara Battaglia]]|ITA}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2013|2013 Cali]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Sandy Scordo]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Nguyen Hoang Ngan]]|VIE}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Sara Battaglia (karateka)|Sara Battaglia]]|ITA}}\n|-\n| [[2017 World Games|2017 Wroc\u0142aw]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Kiyou Shimizu]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Sandra S\u00e1nchez]]|ESP}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Sandy Scordo]]|FRA}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite \u221250 kg====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2013|2013 Cali]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Serap \u00d6z\u00e7elik]]|TUR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Alexandra Recchia]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Maria Alexiadis]]|AUS}}\n|-\n| [[2017 World Games|2017 Wroc\u0142aw]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Alexandra Recchia]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Miho Miyahara]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Serap \u00d6z\u00e7elik]]|TUR}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite \u221253 kg====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1985|1985 London]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Cath\u00e9rine Girardet]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Li Yan (karateka)|Li Yan]]|TPE}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Alba Howard]]|USA}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[C. Sequara]]|VEN}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1989|1989 Karlsruhe]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Cath\u00e9rine Girardet]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Gerlinde Bude]]|FRG}}\n| {{flaga