\n|-\n| [[World Games 1993|1993 The Hague]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Molly Samuel]]|GBR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Annelies Bouma]]|NED}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Irene Lyez]]|AUT}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Sari Nyback]]|FIN}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1997|1997 Lahti]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Chiara Stella Bux]]|ITA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Julliet Toney]]|GBR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Mayuni Baba]]|JPN}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Carmen Garc\u00eda (karateka)|Carmen Garc\u00eda]]|ESP}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2001|2001 Akita]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Karin Prinsloo (karateka)|Karin Prinsloo]]|RSA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Kellie Shimmings]]|AUS}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Roksanda Lazarevic]]|FR Yugoslavia|code=YUG}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2005|2005 Duisburg]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Snezana Peric]]|SCG}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Maria Musall]]|GER}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Lejla Ferhatbegovic]]|BIH}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2009|2009 Kaohsiung]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Mariya Sobol]]|RUS}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Eva Medvedov\u00e1-Tulejov\u00e1]]|SVK}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Ting Chang]]|TPE}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite \u221261 kg====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2013|2013 Cali]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Lina Marcela Gomez Alzate]]|COL}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Jacqueline Andrea Factos Henao]]|ECU}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Olga Malofeeva]]|RUS}}\n|-\n| [[2017 World Games|2017 Wroc\u0142aw]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Alexandra Grande]]|PER}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Anita Serogina]]|UKR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Ingrida Such\u00e1nkov\u00e1]]|SVK}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite \u221268 kg====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2013|2013 Cali]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Kayo Someya]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Ana Maria Escandon Loaiza]]|COL}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Cheryl Kimberly Murphy]]|USA}}\n|-\n| [[2017 World Games|2017 Wroc\u0142aw]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Lamya Matoub]]|ALG}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Alisa Buchinger]]|AUT}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Kayo Someya]]|JPN}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite +60 kg====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1985|1985 London]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Janice Argyle]]|GBR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Rosa Maria Ghidotti]]|ITA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Yvette Bryan]]|GBR}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Stirre Nygaard]]|NOR}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1989|1989 Karlsruhe]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Cath\u00e9rine Belhriti]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Marie-Ange Legros]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Diane Reilly]]|GBR}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Simone Schreiner]]|FRG}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1993|1993 The Hague]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Karin Olsen]]|SWE}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Nurhan Firat]]|TUR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Janice Francis]]|GBR}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Yukiko Yoneda]]|JPN}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 1997|1997 Lahti]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Yukiko Yoneda]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Christina Madrid]]|MEX}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Patricia Duggin]]|GBR}}<BR/>{{flagathlete|[[Michaela Fryblova]]|NOR}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2001|2001 Akita]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Emiko Honma]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Tessy Scholtes]]|LUX}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Tania Weekes]]|GBR}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2005|2005 Duisburg]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Nadine Ziemer]]|GER}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Elisa Au]]|USA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Tania Weekes]]|GBR}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2009|2009 Kaohsiung]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Arnela Od\u017eakovi\u0107]]|BIH}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Tiffany Fanjat]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Silvia Sperner]]|GER}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite +68 kg====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2013|2013 Cali]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Ayumi Uekusa]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Nadege Ait Ibrahim]]|FRA}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Isabel Mallory Aco Bravo]]|PER|state}}\n|-\n| [[2017 World Games|2017 Wroc\u0142aw]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Ayumi Uekusa]]|JPN}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Hamideh Abbasali]]|IRI}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Anne-Laure Florentin]]|FRA}}\n|}\n\n====Kumite open====\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Games}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2005|2005 Duisburg]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Yildiz Aras]]|TUR}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Natasha Hardy]]|AUS}}\n| {{flagathlete|[[Nadine Ziemer]]|GER}}\n|-\n| [[World Games 2009|2009 Kaohsiung]]\n| {{flagathlete|[[Eva 